Youseeme,LordBassanio,whereIstand,
SuchasIam:thoughformyselfalone
Iwouldnotbeambitiousinmywish,
Towishmyselfmuchbetter;yet,foryou
Iwouldbetrebledtwentytimesmyself;
Athousandtimesmorefair,tenthousandtimesmorerich;
Thatonlytostandhighinyouraccount,
Imightinvirtue,beauties,livings,friends,
Exceedaccount;butthefullsumofme
Issumofsomething,which,totermingross,
Isanunlesson'dgirl,unschool'd,unpractised;
Happyinthis,sheisnotyetsoold
Butshemaylearn;happierthanthis,
Sheisnotbredsodullbutshecanlearn;
Happiestofallisthathergentlespirit
Commitsitselftoyourstobedirected,
Asfromherlord,hergovernor,herking.
