Ineverdidrepentfordoinggood,
Norshallnotnow:forincompanions
Thatdoconverseandwastethetimetogether,
WhosesoulsdobearanequalyokeOflove,
Theremustbeneedsalikeproportion
Oflineaments,ofmannersandofspirit;
WhichmakesmethinkthatthisAntonio,
Beingthebosomloverofmylord,
