TheredoIgivetoyouandJessica,
FromtherichJew,aspecialdeedofgift,
Afterhisdeath,ofallhediespossess'dof.
Fairladies,youdropmannaintheway
Ofstarvedpeople.
Itisalmostmorning,
AndyetIamsureyouarenotsatisfied
Oftheseeventsatfull.Letusgoin;
Andchargeusthereuponinter'gatories,
Andwewillanswerallthingsfaithfully.
Letitbeso:thefirstinter'gatory
ThatmyNerissashallbeswornonis,
Whethertillthenextnightshehadratherstay,
Orgotobednow,beingtwohourstoday:
Butwerethedaycome,Ishouldwishitdark,
ThatIwerecouchingwiththedoctor'sclerk.
Well,whileIliveI'llfearnootherthing
SosoreaskeepingsafeNerissa'sring.
